    "Numerical overviews based on categories can only describe the roles of GenAI usage to a certain extent.",
    "As the Romanian example shows, even if there are only a few recorded instances of GenAI use in a country in the database, one instance can still lead to GenAI having a large role [56].Another country for which we found relatively little evidence of GenAI-generated campaigning was Tunisia.",
